Wheeljack-X::

"Did I ever!"  The tall white-and-grey robot pretty much plows his 
way into the appropriate room.  He holds up the vial that contains a 
sample of his work.  "This test tube used to be full of rust."  There 
is no rust evident now, just a thick purple fluid.
